      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is currently in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The engine has a noticeable knock and struggles to maintain idle, while the transmission slips between second and third gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents on the passenger side. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is being sold as-is, ideally for someone looking for a major project or a donor vehicle for parts.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
